## 3. KPI Definitions

| KPI | Definition | Value |
|---|---|---|
| **Total Complaints** | Count of all complaint records | 50,000 |
| **Resolved Complaints** | Count where `Status == 'Resolved'` | 32,473 |
| **Resolution Rate** | Resolved / Total × 100 | 64.95% |
| **Avg Resolution Time** | Mean of `Resolution_Delay_Days` | 8.11 days |
| **High Priority Complaints** | Count where `Priority == 'High'` | 12,433 |
| **Citizen Satisfaction Score** | Mean of `Citizen_Satisfaction_Score` | 2.75 / 5.0 |
| **Complaint Hotspot Zones** | Top zones by complaint count | South-West, Central, Industrial |
| **Department Performance Score** | `0.6×Resolution_Rate% + 0.4×(Satisfaction/5×100) − 0.5×Avg_Delay` | Best: Police Dept · Lowest: Electricity Dept |

